OL,6,FAn inquest into the death of a 13-
OL,7,Fmonth-old from Whitehaven who was
OL,8,Fkilled by the woman who was caring for
OL,9,Fhim has heard that Covid restrictions
OL,10,Fhad a significant impact on his death.
OL,12,FLeiland-James Corkill, from , died
OL,13,Ffrom severe head injuries after being
OL,14,Fshaken.
OL,16,FLaura Castle admitted manslaughter,
OL,17,Fbut following a trial was found guilty
OL,18,Fof his murder.
