OL,6,FAn inquest into his death heard how
OL,7,Fmuch the Castles had relied on their
OL,8,Fparents and other family members' help
OL,9,Fand how this was significantly reduced
OL,10,Fduring the pandemic.
OL,12,FThe inquest found that social care
OL,13,Fvisits were also limited due to Covid
OL,14,Frestrictions.
OL,16,FPenny Hiddle, one of the family's
OL,17,Fsocial workers gave evidence on
OL,18,FTuesday afternoon.
