OL,6,FShe told the inquest she spoke to
OL,7,FLaura Castle while Leiland-James was
OL,8,Fin hospital.
OL,10,FMs Hindle said Castle kept repeating
OL,11,Fthat Leiland-James had fallen from the
OL,12,Fsofa.
OL,14,FShe described how the team had
OL,15,F"believed they were being honest".
OL,17,FThe following day a meeting took place
OL,18,Fwhich showed the injuries could not be
OL,19,Fa result of an accident.
