OL,6,FThe coroner, Dr Nicholas Shaw,
OL,7,Fdescribed how Laura Castle had sent a
OL,8,Fmessage to her husband while he was on
OL,9,Fa night shift.
OL,11,FThe message read "This isn't working.
OL,12,FWe are going to have to ask Penny to
OL,13,Ftake him back."
OL,15,FIndependent safeguarding consultant
OL,16,FNicki Pettitt produced a safeguarding
OL,17,Fpractice review following Leiland-
OL,18,FJames' death.
