OL,6,FShe concluded that "Cumbria County
OL,7,FCouncil followed policy and
OL,8,Fprocedures", adding that his would-be
OL,9,Fadoptive parents were found to be a
OL,10,F"good match" for him.
OL,12,F"Economical with the truth"
OL,14,FHowever, she did point out flaws in
OL,15,Fthe medical and financial checks of
OL,16,Fthe couple, with parts of the
OL,17,Fassessment relying on the couple being
OL,18,Fhonest and declaring debt and mental
OL,19,Fand physical conditions.
