OL,6,F"Much of the system relies on the self
OL,7,Freport of their medical history and
OL,8,Ftheir current health."
OL,10,F"The system relies on adopters being
OL,11,Fopen and honest about their physical
OL,12,Fand mental health."
OL,14,F"They have to provide bank statements
OL,15,F- a bank statement doesn't tell you
OL,16,Fhow much debt you are in."
OL,18,FDr Shaw concluded the Castles had been
OL,19,F"economical with the truth".
